snippet.title: Rooftop Renegade Cyber City Teaser
snippet.description:
Join the Discord! https://discord.gg/2kFGQCj

A trailer highlighting our first game world, Cyber City!

Boost, Grind and Warp through dynamic challenge levels in this high speed racing platformer with both speedrunning challenges and chaotic multiplayer where you take aim and shoot various hazards and traps to slow your opponent down.

Get your kicks!

By Melonhead Games
https://melonheadgames.com.au

Indie Game Platformer Racing Unreal Engine UE4 Epic Shooter
